Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.49,0:28:32.50,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki o megutte{\i0}\N轮回时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.58,0:28:34.00,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ima{\i0}\N如今
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.08,0:28:37.46,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bokura deaeta no{\i0}\N我们终于相遇
