Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.17,0:29:24.42,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sekai ga matteru no{\i0}\N正在等待着你我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.51,0:29:28.34,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Te o totte odorimashou{\i0}\N牵起我的手 一起舞蹈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.43,0:29:30.55,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hajimari no ai{\i0}\N让我们敲响起始的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:32.97,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zu naraseba{\i0}\N你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.06,0:29:35.39,歌词,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Utaou la la la{\i0}\N一起歌唱吧 啦啦啦
